    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a \"difficult time.\" it's like, every time i try to fix something, i just break it more. they’re growing up watching me struggle and fail and be depressed. they’d have so much more freedom if they didn't have to constantly worry about me or try to take care of me. sometimes i think they would actually be happier if i just wasn't around to mess everything up.",
